'''尼敦·亞基'''（{{lang-nl|Nathan Aké}}；{{bd|1995年|2月18日|}}）是一名[[科特迪瓦|科特迪亞]]裔[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]職業足球員，現時效力[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球會[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]，主要司職[[中堅|中堅]]，但也可以作為[[左閘|左閘]]或[[防守中場|防守中場]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Nathan Aké - Detailed stats |url=https://www.transfermarkt.com/nathan-ake/leistungsdatendetails/spieler/177476/wettbewerb/GB1/saison/2018 |work=Transfermarkt |date=2019-05-12 |accessdate=2019-05-28 |language=En |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063008/https://www.transfermarkt.com/nathan-ake/leistungsdatendetails/spieler/177476/wettbewerb/GB1/saison/2018 }}</ref>，为[[荷兰国家足球队|荷兰国家队]]成员之一。

他父親是一名[[科特迪瓦|科特迪亞]]人。

==早期==
亞基出身於他的出生地球會[[ADO海牙|ADO海牙]]，並於12歲時加盟[[飛燕諾|飛燕諾]]青年軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vvwilhelmus.nl/nieuws/2011/december/nathan-ak%C3%A9,-oud-wilhelmus-jeugd-speler,-definitief-naar-chelsea-fc/ |title=Nathan Aké, oud Wilhelmus Jeugd speler, definitief naar Chelsea FC |publisher=V.V. Wilhelmus |accessdate=16 May 2013 |language=nl |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129063009/http://www.vvwilhelmus.nl/nieuws/2011/december/nathan-ak%C3%A9,-oud-wilhelmus-jeugd-speler,-definitief-naar-chelsea-fc/ |archivedate=29 November 2014}}</ref>。

==球會生涯==
===車路士===
亞基在2011年，即加入飛燕諾青年軍4年後，以16歲之齡加盟[[車路士|車路士]]青年軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1340603/Chelsea-lure-15-year-old-Nathan-Ake-spark-Feyenoord-fury.html |title=Chelsea spark Feyenoord fury as Blues lure 15-year-old defender Nathan Ake to London |work=Daily Mail |date=22 December 2010 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063030/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1340603/Chelsea-lure-15-year-old-Nathan-Ake-spark-Feyenoord-fury.html |dead-url=no }}{{Unreliable source?|date=May 2017}}</ref>。
====2012-13====
2012年12月26日，年僅17歲又10個月的亞基首次於[[英超|英超]]亮相，在對[[諾域治城足球會|諾域治]]的比賽的傷停時間後備入替[[桑馬達|馬達]]，車路士最終以1-0勝出<ref>{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Owen |title=Norwich 0–1 Chelsea |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20779143 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=26 December 2012 |archive-date=2013-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130101180041/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20779143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
他在對[[米杜士堡足球會|米杜士堡]]的[[足總杯|足總杯]]比賽中首次為車路士正選上陣<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21515665 "Middlesbrough 0–2 Chelsea"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21515665 |date=20131017130234 }} BBC Sport. 27 February 2013. Retrieved 27 February 2013.</ref> 。
在4月11日的歐霸盃八強第二回合的比賽，亞基再次上陣。雖然球隊以3-2敗筆，但以總比數5-4擊敗來自俄羅斯的[[喀山红宝石足球俱乐部|魯賓卡山]]，晉級準決賽<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/apr/11/rubin-kazan-chelsea-europa-league |title=Chelsea struggle to finish off Rubin Kazan but reach semi-finals |work=The Guardian |date=11 April 2013 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609081826/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/apr/11/rubin-kazan-chelsea-europa-league |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 
亞基於歐霸盃準決賽第二回合對[[巴素爾足球會|巴素爾]]的比賽再次出場，在82分鐘入替[[大衛·雷斯|大衛·雷斯]]，他亦再一次在[[防守中場|防守中場]]的位置出場，協助球隊晉身決賽。在之後對賓菲加的歐霸盃決賽，亞基是後備球員，但沒有上陣，最後車路士勝出決賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/4929206/Benfica-1-2-Chelsea-Match-report-and-pictures.html |title=Benfica 1 Chelsea 2 |work=The Sun |date=15 May 2013 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222190811/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/4929206/Benfica-1-2-Chelsea-Match-report-and-pictures.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 他在季未的球隊頒獎典禮中獲得了最佳年青球員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/javaImages/94/36/0,,10268~11941524,00.jpg |title=Archived copy |accessdate=16 May 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131116205013/http://www.chelseafc.com/javaImages/94/36/0,,10268~11941524,00.jpg |archivedate=16 November 2013}}</ref>，並在英超的最後一個比賽日首次在英超正選上陣，協助球隊以2比1擊敗[[愛華頓|愛華頓]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chelseafc.com/en/matches/match-day/2012/442369?pageTab=lineups|title=Chelsea vs Everton - 2013-05-19 - English Premier League|work=Chelsea Football Club|date=19 May 2013|access-date=2020-06-09|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609081824/https://www.chelseafc.com/en/matches/match-day/2012/442369?pageTab=lineups}}</ref>。

亞基在2013年8月與車路士續約至2018年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/3342358/title/new-deal-for-ake |title=New Deal for Aké |publisher=Chelsea F.C. |date=8 August 2013 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2013-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828034928/http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/3342358/title/new-deal-for-ake |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年10月21日，亞基於車路士主場對陣[[馬里博爾足球俱樂部|馬里博爾]]的分組賽比賽中上演[[歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐聯]]處子戰，於60分鐘後備入替[[法比加斯|法比加斯]]，並且助攻了[[伊登·夏薩特|夏薩特]]的第二個入球<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/29362738 |title=Didier Drogba scored his first goal since rejoining Chelsea as they recorded their biggest Champions League win with a dominant victory against Maribor at Stamford Bridge. |publisher=BBC Sport |date=21 October 2014 |accessdate=21 October 2014 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123092742/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/29362738 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====外借====
在2015年3月25日，亞基被外借到英冠球隊[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]，並於10天後對[[卡迪夫城足球會|卡迪夫城]]的[[英冠|英冠]]比賽中首次上陣<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sportsmole.co.uk/football/reading/team-news/team-news-nathan-ake-handed-reading-debut_215094.html |title=Nathan Ake handed Reading debut |website=''Sportsmole.co.uk'' |accessdate=4 April 2015 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063107/https://www.sportsmole.co.uk/football/reading/team-news/team-news-nathan-ake-handed-reading-debut_215094.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然外借只有短短一個月，但亞基依然於英冠上陣了5次<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.readingfc.co.uk/news/article/royals-sign-nathan-ake-on-loan-from-chelsea-2358756.aspx |title=Royals Sign Nathan Ake on Loan |publisher=Reading F.C. |accessdate=25 March 2015 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901002216/http://www.readingfc.co.uk//news/article/royals-sign-nathan-ake-on-loan-from-chelsea-2358756.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管亞基當季只為車路士出場一次，但時任車路士領隊[[摩連奴|摩連奴]]表示亞基也會獲得英超冠軍獎牌<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espnfc.com/chelsea/story/2450893/jose-mourinho-every-chelsea-player-to-get-prem-medal |title=Every Chelsea player to get a Premier League medal says Jose Mourinho |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2017-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804223651/http://www.espnfc.com/chelsea/story/2450893/jose-mourinho-every-chelsea-player-to-get-prem-medal |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

車路士於8月14日宣布亞基在簽下一份五年合約後，將會在2014-15球季外借到升班馬[[屈福特|屈福特]]
<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.watfordfc.com/news/article/150814-nathan-ake-signs-for-watford-fc-from-chelsea-2619925.aspx |title=OFFICIAL: Aké Joins Hornets On Loan |accessdate=14 August 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221045212/http://www.watfordfc.com//news/article/150814-nathan-ake-signs-for-watford-fc-from-chelsea-2619925.aspx |archive-date=2016-02-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2015/08/new-deal-for-ake.html |title=New deal for Aké |accessdate=14 August 2015 |archive-date=2015-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150816191108/http://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2015/08/new-deal-for-ake.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

11天後，亞基於[[英格蘭聯賽杯|聯賽杯]]第二圈首度為屈福特出場，但卻以1比0輸給英冠球隊[[普雷斯頓足球俱樂部|普雷斯頓]]
<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33969908 |title=Championship Preston reached round three of the Capital One Cup as Marnick Vermijl's goal saw off Premier League Watford, who finished with 10 men |accessdate=25 August 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213222611/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33969908 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 9月19日，亞基在首次為屈福特在英超出場，於比賽尾段後備披甲，為球隊鎖定以2比1擊敗[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/09/19/england/premier-league/newcastle-united-football-club/watford-football-club/2043102/ |title=Newcastle United vs. Watford 1 – 2 (9/19/15) |date=19 September 2015 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063145/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/09/19/england/premier-league/newcastle-united-football-club/watford-football-club/2043102/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。
在12月20日對[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]的比賽中，亞基射入他職業生涯的第一個入球，屈福特最終以3比0擊敗對手<ref>{{cite news |last1=Barlow |first1=Matt |title=Watford 3–0 Liverpool: Nathan Ake capitalises on Adam Bogdan howler and Odion Ighalo strikes to condemn Jurgen Klopp's men to defeat as Hornets move a point off the Premier League top four |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3367794/Watford-3-0-Liverpool-Nathan-Ake-capitalises-Adam-Bogdan-howler-Odion-Ighalo-strikes-condemn-Jurgen-Klopp-s-men-defeat-Hornets-point-Premier-League-four.html |accessdate=21 December 2015 |work=Daily Mail |date=20 December 2015 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063128/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3367794/Watford-3-0-Liverpool-Nathan-Ake-capitalises-Adam-Bogdan-howler-Odion-Ighalo-strikes-condemn-Jurgen-Klopp-s-men-defeat-Hornets-point-Premier-League-four.html |dead-url=no }}{{Unreliable source?|date=May 2017}}</ref>。外借到屈福特期間，亞基主要出現在左後衛的位置。他的表現和態度令他獲得了屈福特的最佳青年球員
<ref name="Watford Award">{{cite news |last1=Barlow |first1=Matt |title=Watford: END OF SEASON AWARDS: Gomes Named 2015/16 Player Of The Season |url=http://www.watfordfc.com/news/article/160517-watford-fc-end-of-season-awards-winners-3116857.aspx |accessdate=5 July 2016 |work=Watford Official Site |date=18 May 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603055221/http://www.watfordfc.com/news/article/160517-watford-fc-end-of-season-awards-winners-3116857.aspx |archive-date=2016-06-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

[[File:Watford_v_Norwich_(8).jpg|thumb]]]]

車路士於2016年6月29日宣布把亞基再次外借，而這次他外借加盟的球會是[[般尼茅夫足球會|般尼茅夫]]<ref>{{Cite news |title=Ake loaned to the Cherries |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2016/06/ake-loaned-to-the-cherries.html?extcmp=SOCIA_TW_ENG_ARTICLES |publisher=Chelsea F.C. |date=29 June 2016 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609091840/https://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2016/06/ake-loaned-to-the-cherries.html?extcmp=SOCIA_TW_ENG_ARTICLES |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亞基的般尼茅夫地標戰是在8月21日，在隊友[[哈里·阿特|哈里·阿特]]紅牌後後備入替[[佐敦·伊比|佐敦·伊比]]。般尼茅夫最終以0比1輸給[[韋斯咸|韋斯咸]]<ref>{{Cite news |title=West Ham United 1–0 Bournemouth |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37075120 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=21 August 2016 |accessdate=21 August 2016 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609081826/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37075120 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 在輸給韋斯咸的比賽後3天，亞基首次為般尼茅夫正選上陣，協助般尼茅夫於聯賽杯第二圈以2-1擊敗[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[摩尔甘比足球俱乐部|摩甘比]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.11v11.com/matches/morecambe-v-afc-bournemouth-24-august-2016-320263/ |title=Morecambe v AFC Bournemouth, 24 August 2016 |date=24 August 2016 |publisher=11v11.com |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813193227/https://www.11v11.com/matches/morecambe-v-afc-bournemouth-24-august-2016-320263/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。
亞基在11月19日，對[[史篤城|史篤城]]的比賽中射入比賽唯一入球，這亦是他為般尼茅夫射入的第一個入球<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37959843 |title=Stoke City 0–1 Bournemouth |date=19 November 2016 |work=BBC Sports |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063159/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37959843 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2016年12月4日，般尼茅夫在只剩15分鐘仍輸3比1的情況下，反勝利物浦4比3，而亞基於93分鐘射入致勝一球，這亦是他的第三個英超入球<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38121184 |title=Bournemouth 4-3 Liverpool - BBC Sport |date=2016-12-04 |work=BBC Sports |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063207/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38121184 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====重返車路士====
車路士於2017年1月8日決定終止亞基的外借
<ref>{{cite news |title=尼敦亞基重返車路士 |url=https://www.goal.com/hk/news/1250/%E8%BB%8A%E8%B7%AF%E5%A3%AB/2017/01/09/31297642/%E5%B0%BC%E6%95%A6%E9%98%BF%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%94%E8%BB%8A%E8%B7%AF%E5%A3%AB |publisher=Goal.com |accessdate=2019年5月29日 |archive-date=2019年5月29日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529034301/https://www.goal.com/hk/news/1250/%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25A3%25AB/2017/01/09/31297642/%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2595%25A6%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25BF%2594%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25A3%25AB |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，並於1月28日對[[巴拉福特足球會|巴拉福特]]的[[英格蘭足總盃|足總杯]]比賽中幫助球隊以4比0輕鬆擊敗對手，完成重返車路士後的地標戰<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=Lythell |date=28 January 2017 |accessdate=28 January 2017 |title=Willian leads impressive Chelsea to big FA Cup fourth round win vs. Brentford |work=ESPN FC |url=http://www.espnfc.co.uk/club/chelsea/363/blog/post/3048506/willian-leads-impressive-chelsea-to-big-fa-cup-fourth-round-win-vs-brentford |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811160710/http://www.espnfc.co.uk/club/chelsea/363/blog/post/3048506/willian-leads-impressive-chelsea-to-big-fa-cup-fourth-round-win-vs-brentford |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 亞基於2月18日的足總杯比賽中再次為車路士上陣，這一次以2比0擊敗[[狼隊|狼隊]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38940092 |title=Wolverhampton Wanderers 0–2 Chelsea |date=18 February 2017 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063218/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38940092 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

4月22日，在[[溫布利球場|溫布利球場]]的足總杯準決賽與[[熱刺|熱刺]]的比賽中，亞基在[[中堅|中堅]]位置與[[大衛·雷斯|大衛雷斯]]和[[施薩·艾斯派古達|艾斯派古達]]一同正選出場，並以4比2擊敗對手，協助車路士進軍決賽<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/39604653 |title=Chelsea 4–2 Tottenham |date=22 April 2017 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613040448/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/39604653 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===般尼茅夫===
亞基於2017年6月30日，正式以2千萬英鎊的轉會費再次加盟[[般尼茅夫足球會|般尼茅夫]]，是當時般尼茅夫的球會紀錄轉會費<ref name="BBC_30Jun2017">{{cite web |title=Nathan Ake: Bournemouth sign Chelsea defender for a club record fee |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40454293 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=30 June 2017 |date=30 June 2017 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063224/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40454293 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===曼城===
亞基於2020年8月5日，以4千1百萬英鎊的轉會費加盟[[曼城足球会|曼城]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Nathan Ake Completes City Switch |url=https://www.mancity.com/news/mens/nathan-ake-signs-63732245 |publisher=Manchester City F.C. |accessdate=5 August 2020 |date=5 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805183548/https://www.mancity.com/news/mens/nathan-ake-signs-63732245 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，簽約5年，將穿6號球衣。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/ake-torres-man-city-numbers-18844945 |title=Man City confirm Nathan Ake and Ferran Torres shirt numbers |accessdate=2020-08-28 |archive-date=2020-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830213528/https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/ake-torres-man-city-numbers-18844945 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==國家隊==
自從亞基在2009年首次代表荷蘭U15國家隊，他已經為荷蘭國家隊所有的青年梯隊上陣了總共54次<ref>{{cite news |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/nathan-ake/182930/ |title=N. AKÉ |publisher=Soccerway |accessdate=26 September 2014 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063252/https://int.soccerway.com/players/nathan-ake/182930/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。他曾是荷蘭U17和U19梯隊的隊長。亞基亦參加了2011和2012年的[[歐洲U-17足球錦標賽|U17歐洲國家盃]]，並分別贏得了兩次的冠軍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uefa.com/under17/news/newsid=1796817.html |title=Captain Aké learns from Chelsea stars |publisher=UEFA |accessdate=14 May 2012 |archive-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914164043/https://www.uefa.com/under17/news/newsid=1796817.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年5月31日，亞基在對[[摩洛哥國家足球隊|摩洛哥]]的國際友誼賽中首次正選出場，並踢滿90分鐘，荷蘭最終以2-1擊敗對手<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-4560108/Morocco-1-2-Holland-Vincent-Janssen-seals-friendly-win.html |title=Ake makes Holland Debut in Friendly |work=Daily Mail |accessdate=1 June 2017 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063236/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-4560108/Morocco-1-2-Holland-Vincent-Janssen-seals-friendly-win.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==技術風格==
亞基控球時的冷靜和他的髮型令很多人都拿他和退役荷蘭、車路士名宿[[古列治|古列治]]作出比較。而他可以在多個不同位置上陣的特性則讓人拿他和[[大衛·雷斯|大衛·雷斯]]比較。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2278552/Chelsea-youth-player-Nathan-Ake-looks-like-Ruud-Gullit-plays-like-David-Luiz.html |title=Ruud boy: Chelsea youth star Ake is a mini Gullit with his dreadlocks and cool head |work=Daily Mail |accessdate=14 February 2013 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063239/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2278552/Chelsea-youth-player-Nathan-Ake-looks-like-Ruud-Gullit-plays-like-David-Luiz.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

亞基曾經表示雖然最近的球季大多數出場的位置是中堅或左後衛，但他最喜歡的位置是中場。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailystar.co.uk/sport/football/526529/Chelsea-Transfer-News-Nathan-Ake-Eddie-Howe-Gossip |title=Premier League boss explains why he has signed this Chelsea defender |work=Daily Star |accessdate=14 July 2016 |archive-date=2019-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529085925/https://www.dailystar.co.uk/sport/football/526529/Chelsea-Transfer-News-Nathan-Ake-Eddie-Howe-Gossip |dead-url=no }}</ref>

